### Create Consent Link
POST http://localhost:8085/admin/links
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: salon-uuid-123

{
  "subject": "customer-uuid-789",
  "policies": ["privacy-policy", "marketing-consent"],
  "expires_in_hours": 48,
  "created_by": "operator-123"
}

